sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as News Edit Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant FS as Media Storage
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open create/update news page
    UI->>LW: mount(article)
    LW->>DB: Load article and translations (if existing)
    DB-->>LW: Existing content
    LW-->>UI: Render multilingual form

    User->>UI: Edit title/content/status/date
    UI->>LW: Update bound properties
    LW-->>UI: Keep form state

    User->>UI: Save article
    UI->>LW: save()
    LW->>DB: Validate and insert/update article + translations
    LW->>FS: Replace cover image if uploaded
    DB-->>LW: Persisted article
    LW-->>UI: Success toast (new: redirect to edit page)
